American Announces
More Nonstops
To London Than Any Other
U.S. Airline.
American Airlines takes great pride in
announcing expanded service to London from
seven American gateways, to both Heathrow and
Gatwick airports. By midsummer, we'll have 12
daily nonstops to Heathrow Airport from New
York Kennedy, Newark, Boston, Chicago, Miami
and beginning July 20, Los Angeles. And daily
nonstops to Gatwick Airport from Dallas/Fort
Worth and New York Kennedy. Our new
service to London, combined with our service
to Manchester, England and Glasgow, Scotland,
will make American the number one U.S. airline
to London and to the entire United Kingdom.
With convenient connections through our U.S.
gateways, flying American is the easy way to
get from your hometown across the Atlantic.
Contact your travel agent or call American
Airlines at 800-433-7300.
